-- triangle-area.cell: triangle area + classification
-- Tests: arithmetic, conditional chains, multi-cell pipeline

‚äĘ compute-area
  given base ‚Č° 6
  given height ‚Č° 8
  yield area

  ‚äĘ= area ‚Üź base * height / 2

  ‚ä® area = 24

‚äĘ classify-size
  given compute-area‚Üíarea
